#

Honey Garlic Glazed Pork Tenderloin

$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Tags:

PorkMain CourseDinner

Description

Tender pork tenderloin glazed with a sweet and savory honey garlic sauce, served with roasted vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Soy Sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh Parsley: for garnish
  • Mixed Vegetables (carrots, bell peppers, broccoli): 2 cups
